Al hadeerah lebanese restaurant is amazing on a Thursday night. Expensive so if you book be sure to not eat all day so you can make the most of the all you can eat food! I love the cocktail roof bar at the one and only royal mirage on an evening! Be sure to have spa treatments somewhere any of the top hotels are good but the one and only royal mirage used to be great! All tourists do the sand dune experience it's fun but if you're not there for long it's not amazing... I'd choose sitting by the pool before that! Atlantis waterpark is amazing!!! As is the ice cream parlour in atlantis... Oh and the steak house in atlantis is SO good but again super pricey. Have an awesome time x
